{"tid":448421,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【閱文狂熱】富途一度乾塘停融資認購 耀才逼爆新開戶市民","createTime":"2017-10-26T07:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T10:12:36.000Z","uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d5fa60a3d460033714d2761ee3255353b9ce710a","tid":448421,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:56:39.000Z","msg":"明星新股閱文（772）首日招股，券商力推融資認購，唯富途率先「爆廠」，未到中午就表示由於認購場面過於火爆，即日暫停槓桿申購，用戶要「抬錢」作現金認購，又稱會緊急申請新額度。至下午近三時，富途再度開放融資額度，支持9倍槓桿認購，指已抬錢作現金認購的客戶，亦可取消後再以融資認購<br />\n<br />\n另外，亦有不少市民趕往証券行開戶，耀才證券觀塘分行現開戶者逼爆情況，大批持開戶文件的散戶需坐於走廊臨時搬出的膠凳，等候開戶手續。<br />\n<br />\n市場消息預料，閱文將凍資近3000億，超越眾安成今年凍資王。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171026/large/1508996222_0fc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171026%2Flarge%2F1508996222_0fc2.jpg&h=91605250&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171026/large/1509002568_b91c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171026%2Flarge%2F1509002568_b91c.jpg&h=1e11c710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n垃圾中資行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf16d403c9d13a2d9e8ea33469a9269c2ee250c","tid":448421,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03c0bce73ee932002d3419b1849d0607b5328cf","tid":448421,"uid":126695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:11:30.000Z","msg":"耀才200億孖展<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7943a40fb258640bd89bd90a354f3af3b8200f2","tid":448421,"uid":56428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re